Steps to create a new dmg

1) ensure the files are in the correct place

1.5) cd into folder

2) update .spec with correct .py file

3) run: 
	
	pyinstaller ThesisTracker.spec

4) test the .app

5) create the dmg folder

	mkdir dmg                     
	cp -R dist/ThesisTracker.app dmg/

6) run this: 

 	hdiutil create \              
  	-volname "ThesisTracker" \
  	-srcfolder dmg \
  	-ov \
  	-format UDZO \
  	ThesisTracker.dmg


	